query:
SELECT MIN(kt.kind) AS movie_kind, MIN(t.title) AS complete_us_internet_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
   comp_cast_type AS cct,
   company_name AS cn,
   company_type AS ct,
   info_type AS it,
   keyword AS k,
   kind_type AS kt,
   movie_companies AS mc,
   movie_info AS mi,
   movie_keyword AS mk,
   title AS t
WHERE kt.id = t.kind_id
AND t.id = mi.movie_id
AND t.id = mk.movie_id
AND t.id = mc.movie_id
AND t.id = cc.movie_id
AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id
AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
AND cn.id = mc.company_id
AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
AND cct.id = cc.status_id
AND cct.kind = 'complete+verified'
AND cn.country_code = '[nl]'
AND it.info = 'tech info'
AND kt.kind IN ('movie', 'tv mini series', 'tv movie', 'tv mini series', 'tv movie')
AND mi.note LIKE '%p%'
AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
AND  (mi.info LIKE '%P%' OR mi.info LIKE '%3%')
AND t.production_year > 2003;

query:
SELECT MIN(kt.kind) AS movie_kind, MIN(t.title) AS complete_us_internet_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
   comp_cast_type AS cct,
   company_name AS cn,
   company_type AS ct,
   info_type AS it,
   keyword AS k,
   kind_type AS kt,
   movie_companies AS mc,
   movie_info AS mi,
   movie_keyword AS mk,
   title AS t
WHERE kt.id = t.kind_id
AND t.id = mi.movie_id
AND t.id = mk.movie_id
AND t.id = mc.movie_id
AND t.id = cc.movie_id
AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id
AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
AND cn.id = mc.company_id
AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
AND cct.id = cc.status_id
AND cct.kind = 'complete+verified'
AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
AND it.info = 'release dates'
AND kt.kind IN ('movie')
AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%'
AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
AND  (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%2007%' OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%')
AND t.production_year > 2000;
